A working prototype of an offline dictionary for Firefox OS.
Builds on https://github.com/rominirani/IndiaPincodesApp.

Build dictionary
================
Obtain file from www.dict.cc, save it as input.txt
$ ./builddict.sh input.txt 20 5 2 dict.dat
Increase numbers until you get no error messages.

Installation
============
Save dict.dat to root directory of SD card of phone.

Use Firefox OS Simulator to install the app contained in the
WebApp folder to your phone.
